OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778605560
OL,3,CSinger Craig David backs Southampton
OL,4,CFC as club speaks out on spying
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FSinger Craig David tells ITV News the
OL,8,Fallegations of spying should not
OL,9,Fdetract from the talent on the pitch
OL,11,FSinger Craig David has backed
OL,12,FSouthampton's chances in their semi-
OL,13,Ffinal EFL clash, as the club asks for
OL,14,Fmore time to investigate allegations
OL,15,Fthey've been spying on their rivals.
OL,17,FThe Saints are accused of unauthorised
OL,18,Ffilming on private property ahead of
OL,19,Ftheir first leg semi-final match
OL,20,Fagainst Middlesborough on Sunday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
