PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778605560
OL,3,CSinger Craig David backs Southampton
OL,4,CFC as club speaks out on spying
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FAhead of their second meeting with the
OL,8,FBoro at home on Tuesday night, the
OL,9,Fclub's CEO Phil Parsons has asked for
OL,10,Fmore time to investigate the
OL,11,Faccusations.
OL,13,FDavid, who was born in the city, said
OL,14,Fit would be a dream come true to be
OL,15,Felevated the Premier League, which
OL,16,Fwould become a step closer if they
OL,17,Fmake it through to the Wembley final
OL,18,Fon Tuesday night.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
