FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778605560
OL,3,CSinger Craig David backs Southampton
OL,4,CFC as club speaks out on spying
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FHe told ITV News the allegations
OL,8,Fshould not distract from the players
OL,9,Fpush for promotion,
OL,11,F"If it becomes something that was the
OL,12,Fcase, the league will deal with it as
OL,13,Fit needs to be dealt with. But I would
OL,14,Flike to think that the players ave
OL,15,Fnothing to do with that.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778605560
OL,3,CSinger Craig David backs Southampton
OL,4,CFC as club speaks out on spying
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,F"The players just want to play
OL,8,Ffootball and do the thing. And when
OL,9,Fyou get on the pitch, even if you know
OL,10,Fany of the tactics that are going on
OL,11,Fwhen you're playing the game, it's a
OL,12,Fcompletely different world.
OL,14,F"I'd like to think that we that the
OL,15,Fgame plays out in the way that it
OL,16,Fshould have played out, regardless of
OL,17,Fwhat's going on in the media."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
