PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778605560
OL,3,CSinger Craig David backs Southampton
OL,4,CFC as club speaks out on spying
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,F"I've been a fan since they were at
OL,8,Fthe Dell behind the Milton Road end,
OL,9,Fwatching the ball flying at the back
OL,10,Fof the net for Matt Le Tissier and
OL,11,FAlan Shearer.
OL,13,F"So to see the chance of them coming
OL,14,Fback up, it will be a dream. And the
OL,15,Fway that they played against Arsenal
OL,16,Frecently and Manchester City was was
OL,17,Ftrue to show true testament of what a
OL,18,Fsquad we've got.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
