PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778605560
OL,3,CSinger Craig David backs Southampton
OL,4,CFC as club speaks out on spying
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FSaints head coach Tonda Eckert left
OL,8,Fthe post-match press conference
OL,9,Ffollowing Saturday's goalless draw
OL,10,Fagainst their North East rivals
OL,11,Fwithout answering questions about the
OL,12,Fallegations.
OL,14,FHis counterpart, Kim Hellberg, said
OL,15,Fafter the first match: "It's a weird
OL,16,Fsituation. I couldn't believe my eyes
OL,17,For ears when heard it, couldn't
OL,18,Fbelieve it when someone told me for
OL,19,Fthe second time or the third.
OL,26,@wD@XOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
